import { IFormValidatorStrategy } from './IFormValidatorStrategy'
import { DemoComponentValidator } from './strategies/DemoComponentValidator'
import { TwitterFeedValidator } from './strategies/TwitterFeedValidator'
import { ContactFormValidator } from './strategies/ContactFormValidator'
import { AdvancedMediaValidator } from './strategies/AdvancedMediaValidator'
import { LiveEventHeadingValidator } from './strategies/LiveEventHeadingValidator'
import { PollValidator } from './strategies/PollValidator'
import { TvFavoriteNoticeValidator } from './strategies/TvFavoriteNoticeValidator'
import { SponsorAdPlacementValidator } from './strategies/SponsorAdPlacementValidator'
import { StrikeGamValidator } from './strategies/StrikeGamValidator'

export class FormValidatorStrategyFactory {
  private static readonly strategies = new Map<string, IFormValidatorStrategy>([
    ['demo-component', new DemoComponentValidator()],
    ['twitter-feed', new TwitterFeedValidator()],
    ['advanced-media', new AdvancedMediaValidator()],
    ['live-event-heading', new LiveEventHeadingValidator()]
    ['poll', new PollValidator()],
    ['tv-favorite-notice', new TvFavoriteNoticeValidator()],
    ['sponsor-ad-placement', new SponsorAdPlacementValidator()],
    ['contact-form', new ContactFormValidator()],
    ['strike-gam', new StrikeGamValidator()]
  ])

  public static build(
    componentName: string
  ): IFormValidatorStrategy | undefined {
    return this.strategies.get(componentName)
  }
}
